{%- block heading %}
## SECTION {{ slNum }} (Maximum Marks: {{ maxMarks }}){.text-center}
{%- endblock %}

{%- block sectioninfo %}
- This section contains **{{ totalQuestions | toWords | upcase }} ({{ totalQuestions | zeroPad: 2 }})** questions.
{%- endblock %}
{%- block questioninfo %}
- Each question has **{{ answerOptions.rows.count | toWords | upcase }}** options {{ answerOptions.rows.chars | joinInEnglish: '(', ')' }}. **ONE OR MORE THAN ONE** of these {{ answerOptions.rows.count | toWords | downcase }} option(s) is(are) correct answer(s).
{%- endblock %}
{%- block eachquestion %}
- For each question, choose the option(s) corresponding to (all) the correct answer(s).
{%- endblock %}
{%- block markingscheme %}
- Answers to each question will be evaluated _according to the following marking scheme_:
  - |-----------------|---|-------------|
    | *Full Marks*    |&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| {{ questionMarks.correct | prepend: '+' }} **ONLY** if (all) the correct option(s) is(are) chosen |
    {%- if questionMarks.partial != 0 %}
      {%- assign remOpt = answerOptions.rows | size %}
      {%- for i in (2..remOpt) reversed %}
        {%- assign chosenOpts = i | minus: 1 %}
        {%- assign marks = chosenOpts | times: questionMarks.partial %}
        {%- if i == remOpt %}
    | *Partial Marks* |&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| +{{ marks }} If all the {{ i | toWords | downcase }} options are correct but **ONLY** {{ chosenOpts | toWords | downcase }} correct options are chosen; |
        {%- else %}
    | *Partial Marks* |&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| +{{ marks }} If {{ i | toWords | downcase }} or more options are correct but **ONLY** {{ chosenOpts | toWords | downcase }} correct options are chosen; |
        {%- endif %}
      {%- endfor %}
    {%- endif %}
    {%- if questionMarks.incorrect == 0 %}
    | *Zero Marks*    |&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| 0 In all other cases. |
    {%- else %}
    | *Zero Marks*    |&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| 0 If none of the options is chosen (i.e., the question is unanswered); |
    | *Negative Marks* {.text-nowrap}|&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| {{ questionMarks.incorrect }} In all other cases. |
    {%- endif %}
    {.no-border}
{%- endblock %}

{%- block examples %}
{%- if questionMarks.partial != 0 %}
{%- assign remOpt = answerOptions.rows | size %}
{%- assign arr = answerOptions.rows.chars %}
{%- assign size = arr | size %}
{%- assign sizeMinusOne = size | minus: 1 %}
{%- assign sizeMinusTwo = size | minus: 2 %}
{%- assign firstPart = arr | slice: 0, sizeMinusTwo %}
{%- assign lastPart = arr | slice: sizeMinusOne %}
{%- assign rowsChars = firstPart | push: lastPart %}
{%- assign rowsCharsCombo = rowsChars | toCombinations | reverse %}

- For example, in a question, if {{ rowsChars | joinInEnglish: '(', ')' }} are the ONLY {{ rowsChars | size }} options corresponding to correct answers, then:
  - choosing ONLY {{ rowsChars | joinInEnglish: '(', ')' }} will get +{{ questionMarks.correct }} marks;
  {%- for comboRow in rowsCharsCombo %}
    {%- assign rowMarks = forloop.rindex | times: questionMarks.partial %}
    {%- for chars in comboRow %}
  - choosing ONLY {{ chars | joinInEnglish: '(', ')'  }} will get +{{ rowMarks }} marks;
    {%- endfor %} 
  {%- endfor %}
  - choosing no option (i.e., the question is unanswered) will get 0 marks; and
  - choosing any other combination of options will get {{ questionMarks.incorrect }} marks.
{%- endif %}
{%- endblock %}
